::Emissary/Organic::

    Emissary was praying to his god, not the Transfor=
mers. He had some new information about his species, they conformed to the =
dominate life on the Planet, but with a definite look of their own, they're=
 goal was to enslave the entire planet and make it a giant Hive.
    Emissa=
ry was in some training simulations and had been proven able to defeat most=
 enemies that the "computer" put forth. His God decided that he could have =
an actual name. He picked one.
    "My name will be Dachande," He said. He =
glanced into a pool of water at his face in humanoid mode, one of his tusks=
 was broken. The name was aptly put, it means "Broken-Knife" (It actually d=
oes, Kinger01030 will know what I mean by that) He took a giant leafish shi=
p that runs on sunlight to move and started out to his ultimate goal, the e=
nslavement of Earth.
